  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n\r\n## Problem \r\nCurrently the amount of unread messages on home tab is reset if open profile from chat view.\r\nReproducible with mentions in public chats.\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nno unread indicator\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nunread messages on tab = 1\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/131094716-1e197b12-1dc4-4006-8862-c1a2ec69c998.mp4\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n1) UserA: add user B to contacts \r\n2) UserB: send a message to userA\r\n3) UserA: open 1-1 chat with userB\r\n4) UserA: open user Profile via options > view User Profile\r\n5) UserA: go back to home view\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: release 1.16 RC1 \r\n- Operating System: Android\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n",
