    "body": "Apparently it is related to some bug in `react-native-navigation` lib. When a modal is opened, bottomTab's state is reset to the state before `{:dotIndicator {:visible false}}` was set. If I dispatch `:change-tab-count` from that modal screen, for instance:\r\n```clojure\r\n(re-frame/dispatch [:change-tab-count :chat {:public 15 :other 20}])\r\n```\r\nThe state is successfully updated, but if I dispatch `{:public 15 :other 20}` it states with previous value. So it seems that `{:visible false}` is ignored in some cases.",
